<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Sellit</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #2C3E50;
            --secondary: #fff;
            --accent: #87CEEB;
            --light: #f0f8ff;
            --dark: #2C3E50;
            --gray: #708090;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .policy-content {
            background: var(--secondary);
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 100px auto 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .policy-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--light);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .policy-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .policy-header p {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .policy-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .policy-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .policy-section h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .policy-section p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .policy-section ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .policy-section li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .contact-info {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .contact-info h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .last-updated {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--light);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .policy-content {
                padding: 20px;
                margin: 80px auto 20px;
            }

            .policy-header h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="policy-content">
            <div class="policy-header">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p>Last updated: September 17, 2025</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>Welcome to Sellit, the University of Ibadan student marketplace. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our platform.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                <h3>Personal Information</h3>
                <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Name and shop name</li>
                    <li>Email address</li>
                    <li>Faculty information</li>
                    <li>WhatsApp contact number</li>
                    <li>Profile pictures and product images</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Usage Information</h3>
                <p>We automatically collect certain information when you use our platform:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>IP address and location data</li>
                    <li>Browser type and version</li>
                    <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
                    <li>Device information</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Provide and maintain our marketplace services</li>
                    <li>Verify user accounts and prevent fraud</li>
                    <li>Facilitate communication between buyers and sellers</li>
                    <li>Send important notifications and updates</li>
                    <li>Improve our platform and develop new features</li>
                    <li>Ensure compliance with our terms of service</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>4. Information Sharing</h2>
                <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information only in the following circumstances:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>With your consent:</strong> When you agree to share information</li>
                    <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Trusted third parties who help us operate our platform</li>
                    <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
                    <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger or acquisition</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
                <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. These measures include:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Encryption of sensitive data</li>
                    <li>Secure server infrastructure</li>
                    <li>Regular security audits</li>
                    <li>Limited access to personal information</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
                    <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct your information</li>
                    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your account and data</li>
                    <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured format</li>
                    <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to certain data processing activities</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
                <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience on our platform. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>Our services are intended for University of Ibadan students and staff. We do not knowingly collect personal information from individuals under 18 years of age.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info">
                <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@sellit.ui.edu.ng</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +234 XXX XXX XXXX</p>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> University of Ibadan, Ibadan, Nigeria</p>
            </div>

            <div class="last-updated">
                This privacy policy was last updated on September 17, 2025.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>